0.0.2.name: wordpress/seo-link-exchange
0.0.2.description: This is a simple plugin to integrate a WordPress site with the SEO link eXchange network. It places a link in the footer or via its own widget and send your link into the SEO link eXchange server to be published on other sites. The network is based on free link exchange. There is no pay version - all the network clients use the network for free.
